intful: Print on Demand\";s:4:\"copy\";s:127:\"Sell custom embroidery and print items without inventory or upfront costs. Start or grow your ecommerce business with Printful!\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:42:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/printful/\";}i:25;a:8:{s:4:\"slug\";s:57:\"product-edit-meta-tab-body-conditional-store-restrictions\";s:7:\"context\";s:26:\"product-edit-meta-tab-body\";s:7:\"product\";s:30:\"conditional-store-restrictions\";s:4:\"icon\";s:73:\"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Recovered.-14.jpg.jpeg\";s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Conditional Store Restrictions\";s:4:\"copy\";s:309:\"Create exclusive members-only stores, wholesale areas, or B2B portals. Conditional Store Restrictions lets you easily control product and category visibility based on User Roles and Countries. Limit access to specific products or entire categories to tailor the shopping experience for every customer segment.\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:64:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/conditional-store-restrictions/\";}i:26;a:8:{s:4:\"slug\";s:41:\"product-edit-meta-tab-body-ticket-checkin\";s:7:\"context\";s:26:\"product-edit-meta-tab-body\";s:7:\"product\";s:14:\"ticket-checkin\";s:4:\"icon\";s:98:\"https://woocommerce.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/QR-Code-Ticket-and-Check-in-for-WooCommerce.png\";s:5:\"title\";s:26:\"QR Code Tickets & Check-in\";s:4:\"copy\";s:269:\"The complete ticketing solution for WooCommerce. Automatically generate unique QR code tickets for any product, deliver them via beautiful HTML emails, and manage check-ins with mobile-friendly QR scanning. Perfect for events, venues, tours, and any ticketable service.\";s:11:\"button-text\";s:10:\"Learn More\";s:3:\"url\";s:48:\"https://woocommerce.com/products/ticket-checkin/\";}}s:7:\"updated\";i:1781606198;}', 'off');
